snippet.title: PS4, NSW & PC | CAPTAIN TSUBASA RISE OF NEW CHAMPIONS
snippet.description: We bring you breaking news straight from the football stadium – enhance your gaming experience through different multiplayer modes with up to four fellow teammates from anywhere on Captain Tsubasa: Rise of New Champions! Coming 28 August 2020 for PlayStation 4, Nintendo Switch and Steam. #BandaiNamco #CaptainTsubasa
